<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>New Roster Published</h1>

    <p>Dear <%= @user.name %>,</p>

    <p>A new roster has been published for your review:</p>

    <div style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #007bff;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;"><%= @roster.name %></h3>
      <p><strong>Published:</strong> <%= @roster.updated_at.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %></p>
      <% if @roster.description.present? %>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong> <%= @roster.description %></p>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <p>Please log in to your account to view the complete roster details and your assigned shifts.</p>

    <p>If you have any questions about your roster, please contact your manager.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>
    The Roster Management Team</p>
  </body>
</html>